  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Welikada jailer arrested with pills",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the police, a jailer of the Welikada prison was arrested by the officers of the Police Special Task Force while trying to bring a suspicious type of pill into the prison.",
        "During the search of the suspected jailer who came to pass through the place where female officers and female inmates were being checked, the police took a suspicious type of pill from the suspect.",
        "At that time, in preparation for the arrest of the suspect, the police said that she immediately snatched the pills from the custody of the police officers and tried to hide them in her mouth.",
        "The police special task force officers who put in a lot of effort arrested the suspect along with the pills.",
        "The pills seized by the police have been submitted to the doctors of the prison hospital for confirmation.",
        "The suspect has been handed over to the officers of second class female jailer M A N Sandamali.",
        "Police Special Task Force Commanding Officer DIG Attorney General Varuna Jayasundara, a team including female police sergeant 1929 Athulathmudali is conducting investigations."
      ],
